compression-zoo — license overview
==================================

This repository aggregates code under several upstream licenses. The
"project glue" — top-level build scripts, this file, the root README,
docs, and other untargeted helper files — is licensed as MIT (text
below). Subdirectories carry their own LICENSE file; that file governs
everything in the subdirectory and overrides this top-level notice.

Per-component licenses
----------------------

  plugins/sdk/         LGPL-2.1+ / BSD-3-Clause (vendored from 7-Zip,
                       Igor Pavlov; see plugins/sdk/LICENSE)
  plugins/zpaq/        MIT for our wrapper code; the bundled libzpaq is
                       public domain (Matt Mahoney). See plugins/zpaq/LICENSE.
  plugins/bsc/         Apache-2.0 (Ilya Grebnov, libbsc). See plugins/bsc/LICENSE.
  plugins/cmix/        GPL-3.0-or-later (Byron Knoll, CMIX). See plugins/cmix/LICENSE.
  rust/sevenz-rs/      LGPL-2.1+ for files that derive from 7-Zip core,
                       public domain for files that derive from the LZMA SDK
                       only. See rust/sevenz-rs/LICENSE.


